Independence is dancing around it. Told that her long-tailed
macaque is illegal in Independence, Mo., Chapman decided to build a
$2,500 monkey house for her beloved Lucy on a neighbor's property
just beyond her back yard _ and just beyond the city limits in
unincorporated Jackson County. And it's no shabby monkey house.
This one has air-conditioning, a skylight and TV. Trisha L. Howard.
17. Photos.
