<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990715.0187 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-15 15:15 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1354 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MORSE-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      07-15 0928
</HEADER>
