kicks into its final crucial weeks. By Dave Anderson.
</P>
<P>
   GLF-BRITISH-OPEN (Carnoustie, Scotland ) _ The first round of
the British Open is a brutal one, with many players shooting in the
80s, and one _ rookie sensation Sergio Garcia of Spain _ actually
shooting an 89. The overall scores for this round may be the worst
for any round of the British Open, or for any of the golf majors.
By Clifton Brown.
</P>
