<HEADLINE>
THE BILLFOLD OF THE FUTURE FOR INTERNET SHOPPERS  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This ``separate buy'' 625-word personal-finance story is from
``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this article, it must be purchased
