   FILM-EYES WIDE SHUT-REVIEW &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ The trailers for Stanley Kubrick's movies are
malicious teases, working audiences into a lather like the work of
no other major director. But in ``Eyes Wide Shut,'' the trailers
promise a wave of humidity that Kubrick has either never been able
to, or wanted to, deliver. In his last picture, Kubrick will have
to get by with a shallow mastery of craft. Accompanied by EYES WIDE
SHUT-ATTITUDE, and STEAMY-MOVIES. By ELVIS MITCHELL. Story will
move in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   EYES WIDE SHUT-ATTITUDE &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ In the past few weeks, Nicole Kidman has appeared nude
on so many magazine covers _ sometimes with also-nude husband Tom
Cruise _ that the couple appear to have renounced their fame and
given their clothing to charity. But don't let Kidman's body-baring
fool you. Although ``Eyes Wide Shut'' is filled with so much nudity
and sexual content that it should've been rated NC-17, it isn't a
very sexy movie _ nor is it intended to be. If anything, this film
_ the last directed by the late Stanley Kubrick _ plays on any
pangs of sexual guilt you might have, with Cruise's character
taking a dark journey through an ever-weirder erotic Wonderland. By
ROBERT PHILPOT. Story will move in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   STEAMY-MOVIES &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Trying to make a list of the hottest movies ever made
is just asking for trouble, because sexual heat is in the eye of
the beholder. Here are some movies provocative enough to keep your
eyes wide open. By ROBERT PHILPOT. Story will move in ``e''
entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   FILM-BLAIRWITCH-REVIEW &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Few pictures sent the kind of excitement through this
year's Sundance Film Festival like the low-tech, no-budget
psychological thriller ``The Blair Witch Project.'' And ``Blair
Witch'' now is jolting the larger landscape with a similar kind of
buzz. By ELVIS MITCHELL. Story will move in ``e'' entertainment
category. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   RODGERS-QANDA &QL;
</P>
