 Here is an updated budget for Focus, which will be available to
clients by 2 p.m. Friday July 16, 1999. For questions call CoxNet
at (404) 526-5456.
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; FOCUS (Available by 2 p.m. Fri., July 16, 1999) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   PAGE INCLUDES FOUR COLOR PHOTOS AND ONE COLOR MAP ILLUSTRATION.
</P>
<P>
   LOST TREASURES OF PERU: Peru's cultural heritage is vanishing
and the causes are many: Greed, poverty, ignorance and vandalism.
Pieces of Peru's rich past are imperiled by numerous threats.
(Includes 2-column color graphic showing areas of Peru, 5-column
color photo of man looking artifacts in the Peru desert, 2-column
color photo of looters running away from authorities, two 1-column
photos of artifacts recovered from Peru.)
</P>
