   GORE-NAACP _ NEW YORK _ Vice President Al Gore addresses the
NAACP convention. (Shepard, Cox News Service). 20.
</P>
<P>
   Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
</P>
<P>
   MANAGED-CARE _ WASHINGTON _ The Senate is scheduled to vote on
competing versions of a ``patients' bill of rights'' regulating the
managed care industry. (Lipman, Cox News Service). 22.
</P>
<P>
   POLITICS
</P>
<P>
   GORE-NAACP _ NEW YORK _ Vice President Al Gore addresses the
