<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-RECYCLED-CLOTHES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   RECYCLED-CLOTHES (Providence, R.I.) will not move in tonight's
New York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, July 15. &QL;
