<P>
   BIZ-WORLD-SKYSCRAPER (Sao Paulo, Brazil) _ Sao Paulo's entry in
the Tallest Skyscraper sweepstakes seems even more a white elephant
than the twin Petromas towers in Kuala Lumpur, and has stirred up a
cyclone of local criticism. By Simon Romero.
</P>
<P>
   With Graphic.
</P>
<P>
   BIZ-SPINOFFS-STOCK (Undated) _ As companies make plans to sell
shares in their Internet operations to the public, they face a
quandary: whether to limit potentially huge stock benefits in the
spinoff to its employees or managers, or to share the wealth
throughout the company. Sholnn Freeman.
</P>
