   &UR; WHO SAID WHAT &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``I only realized the depth of this novel after reading the
Cliffs Notes.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Amazon.com reader comment on ``The Sun Also Rises,'' in a
P.O.V. magazine primer, ``Hemingway, in Just 15 Minutes.''
