<TEXT>
<P>
   CLINTON HOPES BARAK CAN ADVANCE MIDEAST PEACE PROCESS
</P>
<P>
   919. Moving in international and washington categories.
</P>
<P>
   W/PHOTOS
</P>
<P>
   By Bob Deans
</P>
<P>
   Cox Newspapers
</P>
<P>
   WASHINGTON Embracing Israel's new leader as the last hope for
