Israeli took office last week, vowing to move the peace process
forward.
</P>
<P>
   ``He has put peace at the top of his agenda,'' said Clinton,
adding to Barak that ``America will help you as you move forward.''
</P>
<P>
   Barak reciprocated the optimistic sentiment. ``It is our
