<HEADLINE>
GOLF LEADS MICHAELS DOWN THE PATH
</HEADLINE>
 .. CORRECTS HEADLINE TO GOLF (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TOM HOFFARTH  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
